"—I don't know what happened! She just collapsed out of nowhere! We're at..."[r]
I struggled to stay calm as I picked out the right words, stumbling through them while stammering out the address.[l][r]
"Hang in there, Chito! Wake up!" Ms. Ishii shouted, but there was no response.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
[r]"Kanazawa! Where's the AED?!," her head snaps to me.[r]
"My wife's getting it! I've contacted emergency services, too!"[l][r]
I put my hand over my phone as I reply to her.[r]
"Got it!"[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

