Ms. Ishii says nothing as she unbuttons the top of Chito's shirt.[l][r]
The girl lays on the cold floor, pale and unresponsive.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
"One... two... three... four..."[l][r]
Ms. Ishii began to perform a CPR procedure with measured steps and pinpoint precision; she had hoped she'd never have to use it outside of training, yet here she was.[l][r]
Everything looks right; from the vague memories I have of CPR, I think she's doing it correctly.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

